 -+= CLASSIC LINES GAME:

 Try to arrange balls of the same
color in vertical, horizontal or
diagonal lines.
 To move a ball click on it to select,
then click on destination square.

 Once line has five or more balls of
same color, that line is removed and
you earn score points.
 After each turn three balls randomly
added to the board.

 If board filled up, the game is over.
 ____________________
 There are four bonus balls:

    (the Joker) ; can be used with any
     color and multiplys score by x2.

    (the Flush) ; removes all same
     color balls from the board.

    (the Brush) ; paints all nearest
     balls in the one color.

    (the Bomb) ; removes all balls
     in nearest cells.

 ~~~ Good Luck! ~~~
